trans-unit.source: Provides a base class for the design-time functionality of a Web Forms page and allows access to and manipulation of components and controls that are contained within the Web Forms page at design time.
trans-unit.target: Proporciona una clase base para la funcionalidad en tiempo de diseño de una página de formularios Web Forms y permite la manipulación y el acceso a componentes y controles que están dentro de la página de formularios Web Forms en tiempo de diseño.

trans-unit.source: A design host, such as [!INCLUDE[vsprvslong](~/includes/vsprvslong-md.md)], must provide its own derived version of the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebFormsRootDesigner> class to control designers through the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.RootDesigner%2A> property of the designer.
trans-unit.target: Un diseño de host, como [!INCLUDE[vsprvslong](~/includes/vsprvslong-md.md)], debe proporcionar su propia versión derivada de la <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebFormsRootDesigner> clase a los diseñadores de control a través de la <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.RootDesigner%2A> propiedad del diseñador.

trans-unit.source: Control designers use the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.RootDesigner%2A> property to access and manipulate the containing Web Forms page at design time.
trans-unit.target: Controla el uso de diseñadores el <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.RootDesigner%2A> propiedad para tener acceso y manipular la página de formularios Web Forms contenedora en tiempo de diseño.

trans-unit.source: When you inherit from the <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.Design.WebFormsRootDesigner" /> class, you must override the following members:
trans-unit.target: Al heredar de la <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.Design.WebFormsRootDesigner" /> (clase), debe reemplazar los miembros siguientes:

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="P:System.Web.UI.Design.WebFormsRootDesigner.DocumentUrl" />, <see cref="P:System.Web.UI.Design.WebFormsRootDesigner.IsDesignerViewLocked" />, <see cref="P:System.Web.UI.Design.WebFormsRootDesigner.IsLoading" />, <see cref="P:System.Web.UI.Design.WebFormsRootDesigner.ReferenceManager" />, <see cref="P:System.Web.UI.Design.WebFormsRootDesigner.SupportedTechnologies" />, and <see cref="P:System.Web.UI.Design.WebFormsRootDesigner.Verbs" /> properties.
trans-unit.target: El <see cref="P:System.Web.UI.Design.WebFormsRootDesigner.DocumentUrl" />, <see cref="P:System.Web.UI.Design.WebFormsRootDesigner.IsDesignerViewLocked" />, <see cref="P:System.Web.UI.Design.WebFormsRootDesigner.IsLoading" />, <see cref="P:System.Web.UI.Design.WebFormsRootDesigner.ReferenceManager" />, <see cref="P:System.Web.UI.Design.WebFormsRootDesigner.SupportedTechnologies" />, y <see cref="P:System.Web.UI.Design.WebFormsRootDesigner.Verbs" /> propiedades.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="M:System.Web.UI.Design.WebFormsRootDesigner.AddClientScriptToDocument(System.Web.UI.Design.ClientScriptItem)" />, <see cref="M:System.Web.UI.Design.WebFormsRootDesigner.AddControlToDocument(System.Web.UI.Control,System.Web.UI.Control,System.Web.UI.Design.ControlLocation)" />, <see cref="M:System.Web.UI.Design.WebFormsRootDesigner.GetClientScriptsInDocument" />, <see cref="M:System.Web.UI.Design.WebFormsRootDesigner.GetControlViewAndTag(System.Web.UI.Control,System.Web.UI.Design.IControlDesignerView@,System.Web.UI.Design.IControlDesignerTag@)" />, and <see cref="M:System.Web.UI.Design.WebFormsRootDesigner.RemoveControlFromDocument(System.Web.UI.Control)" /> methods.
trans-unit.target: El <see cref="M:System.Web.UI.Design.WebFormsRootDesigner.AddClientScriptToDocument(System.Web.UI.Design.ClientScriptItem)" />, <see cref="M:System.Web.UI.Design.WebFormsRootDesigner.AddControlToDocument(System.Web.UI.Control,System.Web.UI.Control,System.Web.UI.Design.ControlLocation)" />, <see cref="M:System.Web.UI.Design.WebFormsRootDesigner.GetClientScriptsInDocument" />, <see cref="M:System.Web.UI.Design.WebFormsRootDesigner.GetControlViewAndTag(System.Web.UI.Control,System.Web.UI.Design.IControlDesignerView@,System.Web.UI.Design.IControlDesignerTag@)" />, y <see cref="M:System.Web.UI.Design.WebFormsRootDesigner.RemoveControlFromDocument(System.Web.UI.Control)" /> métodos.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.Design.WebFormsRootDesigner" /> class.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa una nueva instancia de la clase <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.Design.WebFormsRootDesigner" />.

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.Design.ClientScriptItem" /> to add to the Web Forms page.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.Design.ClientScriptItem" /> que se va a agregar a la página de formularios Web Forms.

trans-unit.source: When overridden in a derived class, adds a client script element to the current Web Forms page.
trans-unit.target: Cuando se reemplaza en una clase derivada, agrega un elemento de script de cliente a la página de formularios Web Forms actual.

trans-unit.source: The control to add to the Web Forms page.
trans-unit.target: Control que se va a agregar a la página de formularios Web Forms.

trans-unit.target: Control con respecto al cual se agrega <c>newControl</c>.

trans-unit.target: Valor <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlLocation" /> que indica la ubicación de <c>newControl</c> con respecto a <c>referenceControl</c>.

trans-unit.source: When overridden in a derived class, adds a Web server control to the Web Forms page.
trans-unit.target: Cuando se reemplaza en una clase derivada, agrega un control de servidor Web a la página de formularios Web Forms.

trans-unit.source: The ID of the control that was added.
trans-unit.target: Identificador del control que se ha agregado.

trans-unit.source: Although a control might already have an ID assigned to it, if there is already a control in the Web Forms page with the same ID, a new ID is assigned.
trans-unit.target: Aunque un control puede tener ya un identificador asignado, si ya hay un control en la página de formularios Web Forms con el mismo identificador, se asigna un nuevo identificador.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the component that this designer is designing.
trans-unit.target: Obtiene o establece el componente que el diseñador está diseñando.

trans-unit.target: Componente administrado por el diseñador.

trans-unit.target: El <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebFormsRootDesigner.Component%2A> propiedad se establece mediante el <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebFormsRootDesigner.Initialize%28System.ComponentModel.IComponent%29?displayProperty=nameWithType> método.

trans-unit.source: A design host, such as [!INCLUDE[vsprvslong](~/includes/vsprvslong-md.md)], cast as an <see cref="T:System.IServiceProvider" />.
trans-unit.target: Un host de diseño, como [!INCLUDE[vsprvslong](~/includes/vsprvslong-md.md)], convertido en <see cref="T:System.IServiceProvider" />.

trans-unit.source: Returns a design-time <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionService" /> object.
trans-unit.target: Devuelve un objeto <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionService" /> en tiempo de diseño.

trans-unit.source: A design-time designer action service object.
trans-unit.target: Objeto de servicio de acciones de diseñador en tiempo de diseño.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebFormsRootDesigner.CreateDesignerActionService%2A> method is called by a control designer and provides a way for action items for the control designer to be implemented in the Web Forms page through a design host, such as [!INCLUDE[vsprvslong](~/includes/vsprvslong-md.md)].
trans-unit.target: El <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebFormsRootDesigner.CreateDesignerActionService%2A> método llama a un diseñador de controles y proporciona una manera de elementos de acción para el Diseñador de controles que se implementarán en la página de formularios Web Forms a través de un host de diseño, como [!INCLUDE[vsprvslong](~/includes/vsprvslong-md.md)].

trans-unit.source: Returns an <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.IUrlResolutionService" /> that resolves relative URLs.
trans-unit.target: Devuelve un objeto <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.IUrlResolutionService" /> que resuelve direcciones URL relativas.

trans-unit.source: An object that resolves relative URLs.
trans-unit.target: Objeto que resuelve direcciones URL relativas.

trans-unit.source: Gets the culture information for the current thread.
trans-unit.target: Obtiene la información de referencia cultural para el subproceso actual.

trans-unit.target: Información de referencia cultural para el subproceso actual.

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> to release both managed and unmanaged resources; <see langword="false" /> to release only unmanaged resources.
trans-unit.target: Es <see langword="true" /> para liberar tanto recursos administrados como no administrados; es <see langword="false" /> para liberar únicamente recursos no administrados.

trans-unit.source: Releases the unmanaged resources that are used by the <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.Design.WebFormsRootDesigner" /> and optionally releases the managed resources.
trans-unit.target: Libera los recursos no administrados utilizados por <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.Design.WebFormsRootDesigner" /> y, de forma opcional, libera los recursos administrados.

trans-unit.source: When overridden in a derived class, gets the URL at which the Web Forms page is located.
trans-unit.target: Cuando se reemplaza en una clase derivada, obtiene la dirección URL en la que se encuentra la página de formularios Web Forms.

trans-unit.source: The URL at which the Web Forms page is located; otherwise, <see langword="null" />, if the Web Forms page has no associated URL.
trans-unit.target: Dirección URL en la que se encuentra la página de formularios Web Forms; de lo contrario, <see langword="null" />, si la página de formularios Web Forms no tiene una dirección URL asociada.

trans-unit.source: Frees the resources of the current <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.Design.WebFormsRootDesigner" /> object before it is reclaimed by the garbage collector.
trans-unit.target: Libera los recursos del objeto <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.Design.WebFormsRootDesigner" /> actual antes de que lo reclame el recolector de elementos no utilizados.

trans-unit.target: Cuando se reemplaza en una clase derivada, devuelve un objeto <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.Design.ClientScriptItemCollection" /> que contiene todos los elementos de script de cliente de la página.

trans-unit.source: When the <see cref="M:System.Web.UI.Design.WebFormsRootDesigner.GetControlViewAndTag(System.Web.UI.Control,System.Web.UI.Design.IControlDesignerView@,System.Web.UI.Design.IControlDesignerTag@)" /> method returns, <c>view</c> contains an <see langword="IControlDesignerView" /> object that provides access to the visual representation and content of a control at design time.

trans-unit.source: <c>view</c> is passed uninitialized.
trans-unit.target: <c>view</c> se pasa sin inicializar.

trans-unit.source: When the <see cref="M:System.Web.UI.Design.WebFormsRootDesigner.GetControlViewAndTag(System.Web.UI.Control,System.Web.UI.Design.IControlDesignerView@,System.Web.UI.Design.IControlDesignerTag@)" /> method returns, <c>tag</c> contains an <see langword="IControlDesignerTag" /> object that provides access to the HTML element for the control's control designer.
trans-unit.target: Cuando finaliza el método <see cref="M:System.Web.UI.Design.WebFormsRootDesigner.GetControlViewAndTag(System.Web.UI.Control,System.Web.UI.Design.IControlDesignerView@,System.Web.UI.Design.IControlDesignerTag@)" />, <c>tag</c> contiene un objeto <see langword="IControlDesignerTag" /> que proporciona acceso al elemento HTML del diseñador de controles del control.

trans-unit.source: <c>tag</c> is passed uninitialized.
trans-unit.target: <c>tag</c> se pasa sin inicializar.

trans-unit.source: Gets the design-time verbs that are supported by the designer.
trans-unit.target: Obtiene los verbos en tiempo de diseño admitidos por el diseñador.

trans-unit.source: An array of <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerVerb" /> objects supported by the designer; otherwise, <see langword="null" />, if the component has no verbs.
trans-unit.target: Matriz de objetos <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerVerb" /> admitidos por el diseñador; <see langword="null" /> si el componente no tiene verbos.

trans-unit.source: Typically, a design-time environment provides a **Properties** command on a shortcut menu for a component.
trans-unit.target: Normalmente, un entorno en tiempo de diseño proporciona una **propiedades** comando en un menú contextual para un componente.

trans-unit.source: Therefore, do not include a similar entry in the collection of designer-specified verbs.
trans-unit.target: Por lo tanto, no incluya una entrada similar en la colección de verbos de diseñador especificado.
